{"tid":947553,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工已經唔敢飲水唔敢去廁所，但仍然成日犯錯","createTime":"2018-12-19T10:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T14:30:40.000Z","uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8e721373ba9a2c30b4f7e826966d61a9d6732325","tid":947553,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"又話將勤補拙得嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fea5c5072c6bda4f9cafa57e087f0088e220900","tid":947553,"uid":146066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e721373ba9a2c30b4f7e826966d61a9d6732325","tid":947553,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"又話將勤補拙得嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a78f43a9d1bd247bda2d6bb89c2bf8c0f348d92","tid":947553,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"攞定睡袋係公司訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40f8bb716aab1bfd318a071d4c9c22b3650ffbc","tid":947553,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"你拙到勤都補唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f0d0ddfb94b336a8e4adbb08d7856cfe036952","tid":947553,"uid":71237,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"就係因為你無飲水無去廁所搞到狀態唔好先出錯"},{"pid":"1ea022ada06c3e4cf9cf8fff87fca9f0b834e40f","tid":947553,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"日日8AM 做到8PM<br />\n眼很乾很痛"},{"pid":"860b1b6a6a0325b8d3c5e3571a3b6304fadc59ea","tid":947553,"uid":71237,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"認真<br />\n你嘅方向錯咗<br />\n你應該用腦諗下點樣避免錯<br />\n唔去廁所唔飲水唔會提升到工作表現"},{"pid":"ca7854aed5cb6e0f0fae5bac1d174982303ba33b","tid":947553,"uid":191094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過咩原因導致自己犯錯?<br />\n有冇諗下有咩方法令自己唔好再錯?<br />\n諗完有冇做到?<br />\n<br />\n如果返左工冇耐咁都要d時間適應嘅<br />\n如果做左好耐就檢討下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d90ace4f94eb66309fa5e6a42e03ef8bd13c5c","tid":947553,"uid":147892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"平時我番工做野都間唔中會去個廁所<br />\n一來因為我成日飲水防止自己訓著同埋專注啲<br />\n二來當比自己出去行個圈蛇下輕鬆下<br />\n有時對你工作表現可以差好遠<br />\n比如你draft完份野去個廁所番黎睇多次<br />\n可能就會發現邊到有野做錯左"},{"pid":"d3e39b566e3860fd20433888b545fdec6adc9387","tid":947553,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"反而成日行嚟行去<br />\n個人冇咁攰仲爽手咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77706dcf03ddb36dfcf784c2554e256cac46b6e","tid":947553,"uid":187072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:42:18.000Z","msg":"你就係薯仔?"},{"pid":"ec540957be55f3df0c130632f56a034b0b0d78cd","tid":947553,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"拎老綜啦仲返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990dcd60914b2adfab4db5fb6dbf344e88cb1645","tid":947553,"uid":8504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"同巴打一樣 係咁做漏做錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比人小到好灰"},{"pid":"f65f8024f8dcd6e1055e00ee3bf17634833fff33","tid":947553,"uid":113061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊轉新工好驚又做錯"}]}